A "happy hour" is a period of time usually for a few hours after work when bars have lower prices on their drinks and food.
Gary says, "Let me get the waitress, Brenda, so we can order our drinks."
Gary knows the name of the waitress, so he probably goes to the bar a lot.
Shanise says, "Hi, Gary.
